description:
Skin Maker for Minecraft is our new skin creator and editor skins for minecraft. Here you can create your own character or download ready-made skins for minecraft. A huge selection of elements of the minecrafter's wardrobe, the ability to edit the skin, 3d view, create a paper model - all these functions will help you create the perfect skin for minecraft. Create and install skins for minecraft, assemble a 3d model and enjoy the game.

You can save minecraft skins in different formats to build blocks on any version of the game. You can create a paper model of the skin, print it out, cut it out and glue it for a real minecraft game. Also, do not forget to record a video and share the process of creating skins for minecraft with familiar players.

Skins for minecraft functionality:
1. Skin Maker for Minecraft:
- Ability to draw a skin for minecraft from scratch;
- A huge minecrafter's wardrobe;
- More than 7000 ready-made skins in sets that can be diversified;
- Wide palette of colors;
- View character in 3d.
The skin creator allows you to translate your ideas into original character images. Skin tone, eyes, hair, hats, t-shirts and pants. Every time you will get new minecrafters - video-making youtuber skins, world-saving superhero skins, girl skins in summer hats, boy skins in stylish jeans, camouflage skins, herobrines, mobs and many others.

2. Edit Skins for Minecraft:
- Skin editor minecrafter skins;
- Loading ready-made characters from the device;
- 360 degree view;
- Large selection of editing tools;
- Reset settings to the initial level.
Open the skin editor and dive into the creative process. Change colors, match clothes and add new elements. A palette, pipette, fill, pencil and other tools will help you create the perfect minecrafter skin. Experience the character from all angles in 3D, then save the ready-made skins of girls and boys to your device.

3. Paper Model Skin for Minecraft:
- Ability to make skins out of paper;
- Print skin image;
- Easy model assembly, gluing.
Creation of a paper skin model for a real minecraft game. Print, cut, glue the parts and call your friends. Boy skins can fight enemies and girl skins can build beautiful fortresses.

4. Other features:
- Record video of creating skins to show to friends or publish on social networks;
- Selecting and loading a background image;
- Gallery of skins in the application;
- Save the skin on the device;
- 3d view in full screen;
- 29 themed skin packs, including over 7000 skins.
The skin editor offers a variety of backgrounds, including an image from the device. The process of creating a character can be recorded on the built-in camera, and then save the result and share the video on social networks. If you have any problems in the application, write about it by mail and we will consider your message in new updates.

5. Unlimited access:
- Access to sets of skins without restrictions;
- Ability to add background image from device gallery
- Skin maker without ads.

6. Skins for minecraft are already waiting for you!
A lot of themed sets will not make you think for a long time which character for minecraft will look better. Superheroes, Halloween, mobs, mermaids, monsters, girls, boys, anime, youtubers, characters of popular computer games and TV shows, cartoon characters - this and much more is waiting for you in one application. Skins for minecraft will help you draw a skin for minecraft yourself, install it and go into battle on the map or over the network. You can always save the finished work in the gallery or on your device, and then print and assemble a paper minecraft skin.

