Minecraft Live Wallpaper is an application in which you can customize wallpapers with moving pixel objects from the game: picks, hearts, swords, shovels, skins and much more. 3D wallpapers in the style of Minecraft will become the original background for your device. A large collection of items and wide settings will give you a lot of personalized options to set live wallpapers in the Minecraft style.

Live Wallpaper Settings:
- unlimited number of 3D objects moving on the screen;
- customize the background color from a multi-thousand color palette;
- selection of the size of the elements;
- setting the transparency of objects;
- adjust the brightness of objects;
- the speed of movement on the screen;
- adding highlights.

After setting up, you will be able to preview your live wallpaper before installing and edit what you didn't like. You can install live wallpapers on your phone both on the main screen of the device and on the lock screen.

In the gallery of moving elements from the game you will find:
- skins;
- food;
- objects of the game environment;
- picks, swords and shovels;
- and many more interesting things.

Stand out with the help of original and stylish live wallpapers in the style of Minecraft. Enjoy personal minecraft wallpapers every time you use your smartphone. Share your find with your friends and compete who will turn out more beautiful. Write your wishes about how you would like to see our application Live Wallpaper in the style of Mancraft to us by mail. We are always happy to receive your feedback! 

